mainText: Jul 18 Nordstrom Anniversary Sale Favorites It's July, which means one of the best honorary national holidays of the year is here: The Nordstrom Anniversary Sale! I scoured the Nordstrom site in search of the prettiest pieces and listed my favorites below for you. With so many great pieces on sale, be sure to sign up for Early Access to get your first choice picks and before prices go up on August 8th. They’re also offering in-store pickup for online orders, which is a great way to shop in comfort and avoid all the crowds! Take me on Instagram with #LSNordSale so I can see all the pretty new additions to your closet! Happy Shopping! 1.) Ralph Lauren/ Collarless Crepe Topper Coat Other gorgeous coats: Ralph Lauren/ Black Wool Maxi Bebe/ Grey Tweed Wrap Coat 2.) Leith/Mock Neck Midi Dress (also in pink!) More dresses here: O'Neill Print Sheath Dress ASTR Stripe Romper 3.) Ted Baker London/ ‘Crystal Bobble’ Patent Leather Clutch (also in floral) Handbags/Clutches: Ted Baker/ Leather Satchel Vince Camuto/ 'Abril' Leather Shoulder Bag Rebecca Minkoff/ 'Avery' Crossbody Bag Leather Weekender: Sole Society/ 'Cassidy' Faux Leather Duffel Bag 4.) Topshop/ 'Julie' Suede Moto Jacket 5.) Topshop/ Shiny Quilted Bomber Jacket 6.) Maia/ Floral Print Scuba Knit Sheath Dress 7.) Lyssé High Waist Faux Leather Leggings, Citizens of Humanity/ 'Rocket' High Rise Distressed Skinny Jeans 8.) Rebecca Minkoff/ 'Large Regan’ Satchel 9.) Fendi/ 52mm Cat Eye Sunglasses, Dior 'So Real' 48mm Sunglasses 10.) Halogen/ 'Owen' Genuine Calf Hair Pointy Toe Ghillie Flat 11.) Nike/ 'Juvenate’ Sneaker 12.) Charles by Charles David/ 'Lyssa' Over the Knee Boot I also love these boots: Stuart Weitzman 'Soho' Tall Elastic Back Boot (such a great deal!) Dolce Vita/'Connor' Over the Knee Western Boot 13.) Chloé/ Eau de Parfum Spray Set One of my favorite scents: Viktor&Rolf 'Flowerbomb' Eau de Parfum Set 14.) Butter LONDON/ 'Wanderlust' Nail Lacquer Collection More beauty products: Love a nude lip: Bobbi Brown 'Bobbi on Trend - Nude Lips' Set I loved Mario Badescu skincare products! Start your obsession with this starter set: 'Icon, The Cult Favorite & The Hero' Set 15.) Kate Spade/ Calf hair Leopard Belt 16.) Cristabelle/ 'Anni' Crystal Bib Necklace 17.) Movado/ 'Bold' Round Bracelet Watch, 36mm 18.) Cristabelle/ Crystal Ear Crawlers 19.) Cristabelle/ 'Anni' Crystal Ear Jackets Easily the best product in the sale- a rose gold flamingo pool float! I mean, how can you not love this! Aileen Rathee Subscribe to my latest looks! Be the first the see the latest looks or blogs from the Lookbook! SIGN UP Recently from the Lookbook Jan 7, 2019 Aileen YSL Studio Paris, France Find me on @Instagram @_lovelysunday

paragraphs: It's July, which means one of the best honorary national holidays of the year is here:

I scoured the Nordstrom site in search of the prettiest pieces and listed my favorites below for you. With so many great pieces on sale, be sure to sign up for Early Access to get your first choice picks and before prices go up on August 8th. They’re also offering in-store pickup for online orders, which is a great way to shop in comfort and avoid all the crowds!
Take me on Instagram with #LSNordSale so I can see all the pretty new additions to your closet!
1.) Ralph Lauren/ Collarless Crepe Topper Coat
2.) Leith/Mock Neck Midi Dress (also in pink!)
3.) Ted Baker London/ ‘Crystal Bobble’ Patent Leather Clutch (also in floral)
Sole Society/ 'Cassidy' Faux Leather Duffel Bag
6.) Maia/ Floral Print Scuba Knit Sheath Dress
7.) Lyssé High Waist Faux Leather Leggings, Citizens of Humanity/ 'Rocket' High Rise Distressed Skinny Jeans
9.) Fendi/ 52mm Cat Eye Sunglasses, Dior 'So Real' 48mm Sunglasses
10.) Halogen/ 'Owen' Genuine Calf Hair Pointy Toe Ghillie Flat
12.) Charles by Charles David/ 'Lyssa' Over the Knee Boot
I also love these boots: Stuart Weitzman 'Soho' Tall Elastic Back Boot (such a great deal!)
Dolce Vita/'Connor' Over the Knee Western Boot
13.) Chloé/ Eau de Parfum Spray Set
One of my favorite scents: Viktor&Rolf 'Flowerbomb' Eau de Parfum Set
Love a nude lip: Bobbi Brown 'Bobbi on Trend - Nude Lips' Set
I loved Mario Badescu skincare products! Start your obsession with this starter set:
'Icon, The Cult Favorite & The Hero' Set
15.) Kate Spade/ Calf hair Leopard Belt
Easily the best product in the sale- a rose gold flamingo pool float! I mean, how can you not love this!
